roblem, a WDM model with R_f~0.16 Mpc (m_w~0.75 kev; flat\ncosmology with Omega_L=h=0.7) also predicts concentrations, a Tully-Fisher\nrelation, and formation epochs for small halos which seems to be in better\nagreement with observations, relative to CDM predictions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Oct 2000 22:36:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 27 Oct 2000 03:43:15 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 8 Jun 2001 14:11:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-09-25"}
