ed and significant\ncorrections are identified.We show also that for values of $\\kappa_t$ achieved\nat fixed target energies, di-jet production by the e.m. field of the nucleus\nleads to an insignificant correction which gets more important as $\\kappa_t$\nincreases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Oct 2000 23:35:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 29 Jan 2002 22:15:46 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 31 Mar 2002 18:22:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-31"}
